reviewText: Esta pelicula merece ser considerada una de las mejores del cine mexicano. La vi en el cine cuando se estreno' en 1984 y reciente la compre' aqui en Amazon.

LOVE VICENTE. And his MOVIES. Work at a Nursing home and your little spanish speeking Residents love his movies. I makes me feel good to see them remember when they use to go see his movies in their younger years. Thank You.
